            <title>[LU-12427] LNet MR routing: output a warning if discovery is off</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12427</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Although MR routing works with discovery is off. It is ideal to keep discovery on. In this way the internal peer database has an accurate view of the gateway&apos;s interfaces.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you attempt to add a route and discover is off, output a warning that discovery is off&lt;/p&gt;</description>
